sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (EHR Dashboard)
    participant G as Flask API Gateway
    participant V as Token Vault (Redis)
    participant L as External LLM API
    C->>G: POST /api/redact (Raw Note)
    G->>G: Rate limit check & validate note size
    G->>G: Execute Hybrid Regex/NLP Scan
    G->>G: Resolve overlapping spans
    G->>V: Store original values & return sequential tokens
    V-->>G: Redacted Note (Tokens embedded)
    G->>L: POST /api/ask (Redacted Note)
    L-->>G: Response (Summary with Tokens)
    G->>V: Restore original identities
    V-->>G: Fully restored summary response
    G-->>C: JSON response with stats & restored text